1. Decide where to order the pizza from
2. Decide what kind of pizza to order
3. Go to the restaurant's website
4. Go to the menu
5. Find the pizza you want
6. Click on the pizza
7. Make any desired adjustments to the pizza
    eg no mushrooms, add pineapple
8. Add the pizza to your order
9. Go to checkout
10. Enter your address details
11. Enter your payment details
12. Click order
13. Wait until driver comes to your location
14. Put barking dog in other room
15. Receive pizza
16. Tip driver
17. Get a drink or make a drink
18. Eat your pizza

NOTE: Save homework for after pizza!